00:20:03.270 --> 00:20:05.350
an abandoned baby from a poor family.

00:20:06.310 --> 00:20:07.030
In Yu County,

00:20:08.310 --> 00:20:09.590
I had a privileged life

00:20:09.680 --> 00:20:12.440
